'''Marc Bauman''' portrayed the [[Corellia Star captain|captain]] of the ''[[Corellia Star]]'' as well as a [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Stormtrooper]] in [[Star Wars: Rebel Assault II: The Hidden Empire|''Rebel Assault II'']]. He also played a [[Unidentified B-wing pilot|B-wing pilot]] in the game's trailer.

